116
00:11:37,033 --> 00:11:40,617
protracenih uzalud.

117
00:11:46,631 --> 00:11:47,700
Nastavite.

118
00:11:48,271 --> 00:11:49,818
Dve gvineje.

119
00:11:50,031 --> 00:11:53,181
Dragi Prospero, zašto ste me napustili?

120
00:11:54,750 --> 00:11:59,494
Hrabar u Parlamentu, a za stolom miš.

121
