Meni je ostalo još 10 gvineja.

123
00:12:14,347 --> 00:12:16,690
Znaci 10.

124
00:12:16,907 --> 00:12:19,011
Izlaziš ili ostaješ, Wilberforce?

125
00:12:29,825 --> 00:12:31,565
Olovku i papir.
- Ne, ne, ne.

126
00:12:31,785 --> 00:12:34,333
To je pravilo kuce <i>Brooks's Club</i>.

127
