153
00:15:23,318 --> 00:15:25,343
Secaš li se, Billy, na Cambridge-u

154
00:15:25,559 --> 00:15:28,265
imao sam reputaciju pevaca?

155
00:15:28,478 --> 00:15:30,218
Secam se.

156
00:15:30,438 --> 00:15:33,180
Mislim da cu otici i otpevati im pesmu.

157
00:15:43,076 --> 00:15:46,738
Tišina!

158
00:15:48,155 --> 00:15:49,975
Tišina!

159
00:15:53,595 --> 00:15:57,257
Zvucite kao neki gadni hor macaka.

160
00:15:57,474 --> 00:16:02,468
Da vas upoznam sa nekim
ko to radi na pravi nacin.

161
00:16:06,152 --> 00:16:08,416
Posvecujem ovu pesmu
mom casnom prijatelju,

162
00:16:08,632 --> 00:16:11,862
