174
00:18:27,411 --> 00:18:30,153
Ne tice me se, gospodine.

175
00:18:30,371 --> 00:18:32,316
Istina je, uh...

176
00:18:35,250 --> 00:18:39,960
malo sam cudniji nego obicno
u poslednje vreme, zar ne?

177
00:18:40,170 --> 00:18:41,637
